  "title": "✈️🌍 Travel & Brand Ambassador | No Experience Needed",
  "description": "<p>🎓Just graduated? Switching careers? <strong>No problem!</strong></p><p> Gain hands-on experience, fast career growth, and travel opportunities while representing top brands.<br /></p><h3>🔥 <strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li>Engage customers at events, roadshows, and residential areas</li><li>Represent client brands professionally and confidently </li><li>Support sales and marketing campaigns to achieve targets</li><li>Participate in team training, planning, and brainstorming</li><li>Progress into leadership roles based on performance<br /></li></ul><h3>✨ <strong>Why Join Us</strong></h3><ul><li>1-on-1 mentorship and structured training provided</li><li>Performance-based earnings with weekly payouts & uncapped incentives 💸</li><li>Clear career progression based on results and capability 📈</li><li>Local and regional travel opportunities ✈️</li><li>Supportive, goal-driven team environment 🤝</li></ul><p><br />📩 <strong>Apply now</strong> to kickstart your career with real growth and real exposure.</p>",
